    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Exercices Semaine 4\"\nformat:\n  html:\n    html-math-method: mathjax\n    includes:\n      in_header: |\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\" async\n          src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\">\n        </script>\ntoc: false\neditor: source\n---\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\n<!-- JavaScript -->\n\n\n\n\n```{=html}\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\nfunction toggleAlert(event, message, type) {\n  var alertBox = event.target.nextElementSibling; // Select the alert box next to the clicked button\n  var alertMessage = alertBox.querySelector(\".alertMessage\");\n  var alertType = alertBox.querySelector(\".alertType\");\n\n  if (alertBox.style.display === \"block\") {\n    alertBox.style.display = \"none\"; // Hide the alert box if it's already visible\n  } else {\n    alertMessage.innerHTML = message;\n    alertType.innerHTML = (type === 'hint') ? '‚ùì Indice' : 'üí° Explication';\n\n    // Change style based on type (yellow for hint, green for explanation)\n    alertBox.style.backgroundColor = (type === 'hint') ? '#FFEDA3' : '#C0EDC2';  \n    alertBox.style.borderColor = (type === 'hint') ? '#E5B800' : '#388E3C';  \n    alertBox.style.display = \"block\";  // Show the alert\n\n    MathJax.typesetPromise([alertMessage]);  // Re-render math with MathJax v3\n  }\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n\n\n\n<!-- CSS for Styling -->\n\n\n\n\n```{=html}\n<style>\n/* Custom styles for the buttons */\n.custom-button {\n  border: none;\n  padding: 10px 20px;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  color: black;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.1s ease;\n}\n\n/* Green button for Explanation */\n.explanation {\n  background: #C0EDC2; /* Green */\n  border: 2px solid #388E3C; /* Slightly darker green */\n}\n\n.explanation:hover {\n  background: #388E3C; /* Darker green */\n  transform: scale(1.08);\n}\n\n/* Yellow button for Hint */\n.hint {\n  background: #FFEDA3; /* Yellow */\n  border: 2px solid #E5B800; /* Slightly darker yellow */\n}\n\n.hint:hover {\n  background: #E5B800; /* Darker yellow */\n  transform: scale(1.08);\n}\n\n/* Custom styles for the alert box */\n.alert {\n  padding: 15px;\n  color: black;\n  margin-top: 10px; /* Ensure spacing between button and alert */\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  border: 2px solid;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  width: fit-content; /* Prevent full-width alerts */\n}\n</style>\n```\n\n\n\n\n<!-- MathJax for Rendering Math -->\n\n\n\n\n```{=html}\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" async\n  src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/3.2.2/es5/tex-mml-chtml.js\">\n</script>\n```\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n## Question 1\n\nL'expression \\\\(\\\\frac{n!}{(n-2)!}\\\\) est √©quivalente √†:\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_ZZAUNLVSWT'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZZAUNLVSWT\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(n^3 - n\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZZAUNLVSWT\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{n^2 - n}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZZAUNLVSWT\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(n\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZZAUNLVSWT\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(n^2 - n\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Simplifiez le terme \\\\(\\\\frac{n!}{(n-2)!}\\\\).', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'L‚Äôexpression \\\\(\\\\frac{n!}{(n-2)!}\\\\) se simplifie en \\\\(n \\\\times (n-1)\\\\), ce qui donne \\\\(n^2 - n\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n## Question 2\n\nSi \\\\( X \\\\sim \\\\text{Bin}(10, 0.5)\\\\), quelles sont respectivement \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X)\\\\) et \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X)\\\\) ?\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_VRYICMLEID'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_VRYICMLEID\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 5\\\\) et \\\\( \\\\text{Var}(X) = 2.5\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_VRYICMLEID\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 3\\\\) et \\\\( \\\\text{Var}(X) = -2\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_VRYICMLEID\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 2\\\\) et \\\\( \\\\text{Var}(X) = 5\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_VRYICMLEID\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\( \\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 3\\\\) et \\\\( \\\\text{Var}(X) = 0\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_VRYICMLEID\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 5\\\\) et \\\\( \\\\text{Var}(X) = 2.5\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Rappelez-vous que pour une distribution binomiale \\\\(X \\\\sim \\\\text{Bin}(n, p)\\\\), l‚Äôesp√©rance \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X)\\\\) est \\\\(np\\\\) et la variance \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X)\\\\) est \\\\(np(1-p)\\\\).', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Pour une distribution binomiale \\\\(X \\\\sim \\\\text{Bin}(10, 0.5)\\\\), l‚Äôesp√©rance \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X)\\\\) est \\\\(10 \\\\times 0.5 = 5\\\\) et la variance \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X)\\\\) est \\\\(10 \\\\times 0.5 \\\\times (1-0.5) = 2.5\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n## Question 3\n\nSoit \\\\(X\\\\) le temps d'attente en seconde lors d'un appel √† un centre t√©l√©phonique. On consid√®re que \\\\(X \\\\sim U(0,120)\\\\). Quelle est la probabilit√© que vous attendiez moins de \\\\(40\\\\) secondes?\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_CNSRJLYERP'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CNSRJLYERP\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CNSRJLYERP\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{3}{5}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CNSRJLYERP\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{5}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CNSRJLYERP\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_CNSRJLYERP\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{2}{3}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Rappelez-vous que pour une distribution uniforme \\\\(U(a, b)\\\\), la probabilit√© qu‚Äôune valeur soit inf√©rieure √† un certain seuil est donn√©e par la proportion de l‚Äôintervalle couvert par ce seuil.', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Pour une distribution uniforme \\\\(X \\\\sim U(0, 120)\\\\), la probabilit√© que \\\\(X\\\\) soit inf√©rieur √† \\\\(40\\\\) secondes est de \\\\(40 \\\\times \\\\frac{1}{120 - 0} = \\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n## Question 4\n\n√âtant donn√© le m√™me contexte que la question \\\\(3\\\\), quelle est la probabilit√© que vous attendiez plus d'une minute?\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_WGWTJGHQAI'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WGWTJGHQAI\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WGWTJGHQAI\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{2}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WGWTJGHQAI\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{2}{5}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WGWTJGHQAI\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WGWTJGHQAI\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{3}{5}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Rappelez-vous que pour une distribution uniforme \\\\(U(a,b)\\\\), la probabilit√© qu\\'une valeur soit sup√©rieure √† un certain seuil est donn√©e par la proportion de l\\'intervalle restant apr√®s ce seuil. Dans ce cas, calculez la proportion du temps restant apr√®s \\\\(60\\\\) secondes dans l\\'intervalle total de \\\\(120\\\\) secondes.', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Pour une distribution uniforme \\\\(X \\\\sim U(0, 120)\\\\), la probabilit√© que \\\\(X\\\\) soit sup√©rieur √† \\\\(60\\\\) secondes est de \\\\( 1 - 60  \\\\times \\\\frac{1}{120 - 0} = \\\\frac{1}{2}\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n## Question 5\n\n√âtant donn√© le m√™me contexte que la question \\\\(3\\\\), quelle est la probabilit√© que vous attendiez entre une minute et une minute et trente seconde?\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_ZIEGDLDDKS'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZIEGDLDDKS\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZIEGDLDDKS\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{2}{3}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZIEGDLDDKS\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{1}{4}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZIEGDLDDKS\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{2}{5}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZIEGDLDDKS\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{3}{4}\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_ZIEGDLDDKS\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\frac{3}{5}\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Rappelez-vous que pour une distribution uniforme \\\\(U(a,b)\\\\), la probabilit√© qu\\'une valeur se situe entre deux seuils est donn√©e par la proportion de l\\'intervalle entre ces deux seuils. Dans ce cas, calculez la proportion du temps entre \\\\(60\\\\) secondes (\\\\(1\\\\) minute) et \\\\(90\\\\) secondes (\\\\(1\\\\) minute et \\\\(30\\\\) secondes) dans l\\'intervalle total de \\\\(120\\\\) secondes.', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Pour une distribution uniforme \\\\(X \\\\sim U(0, 120)\\\\), la probabilit√© que \\\\(X\\\\) soit sup√©rieur entre \\\\(90\\\\) secondes et \\\\(60\\\\) secondes est de \\\\( 90  \\\\times \\\\frac{1}{120 - 0}  - 60  \\\\times \\\\frac{1}{120 - 0} =  30  \\\\times \\\\frac{1}{120 - 0} = \\\\frac{1}{4} \\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n## Question 6\n\n√âtant donn√© le m√™me contexte que la question \\\\(3\\\\), quelle est l'esp√©rance et la variance de \\\\(X\\\\)?\n\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_PCCXJNGCXX'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_PCCXJNGCXX\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 60\\\\) et \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = 1500\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_PCCXJNGCXX\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 30\\\\) et \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = 600\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_PCCXJNGCXX\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 60\\\\) et \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = 600\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_PCCXJNGCXX\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 120\\\\) et \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = 1200\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_PCCXJNGCXX\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X) = 60\\\\) et \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = 1200\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Rappelez-vous que pour une distribution uniforme \\\\(U(a, b)\\\\), l‚Äôesp√©rance est \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X) = \\\\frac{a + b}{2}\\\\) et la variance est \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = \\\\frac{(b - a)^2}{12}\\\\).', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Pour une distribution uniforme \\\\(X \\\\sim U(0, 120)\\\\), l‚Äôesp√©rance est \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X) = \\\\frac{0 + 120}{2} = 60\\\\) et la variance est \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = \\\\frac{(120 - 0)^2}{12} = 1200\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n**Surveillance d‚Äôun trait√© de d√©sarmement**\n\nUn trait√© de d√©sarmement impose des restrictions sur la production d‚Äôarmes dans un pays. Un organisme international m√®ne des inspections surprises. On estime que la probabilit√© qu‚Äôune inspection d√©tecte une violation est seulement de \\\\(2 \\\\%\\\\). \n\n## Question 7\n\nSi l‚Äôorganisme r√©alise \\\\(20\\\\) inspections ind√©pendantes, quelle est la probabilit√© qu‚Äôau moins une inspection d√©tecte une violation ? Les probabilit√©s sont arrondies au dixi√®me le plus proche.\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_BRDWQFPSMN'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BRDWQFPSMN\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.73\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BRDWQFPSMN\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.06\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BRDWQFPSMN\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.33\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BRDWQFPSMN\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.94\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Pensez √†  \\'\\'prendre la route la plus courte\\'\\'.', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, '\\\\(P(X\\\\geq 1) = 1- P(X=0) = 1 - C^0_{20}(0.02)^0(0.98)^{20} = 1-0.98^{20}=1-0.67=0.33\\\\). Revoir diapositives du cours \\\\(4\\\\), page \\\\(15\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n## Question 8\n\nCombien d'inspection (ind√©pendantes) l‚Äôorganisme devrait-il r√©aliser pour que la probabilit√© de d√©tecter au moins une violation soit sup√©rieure ou √©gale √† \\\\(80 \\\\%\\\\) (avant d'arrondir) ? \n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_URZWVUOLHA'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_URZWVUOLHA\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(20\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_URZWVUOLHA\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(70\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_URZWVUOLHA\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(79\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_URZWVUOLHA\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(80\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_URZWVUOLHA\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(90\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Ici il s\\'agit de tester les diff√©rentes valeurs. Pensez √† \\'\\'prendre la route la plus courte\\'\\' comme dans l\\'exercice pr√©c√©dent.', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'On d√©note par \\\\(X_n\\\\) une variable al√©atoire binomiale avec \\\\(n\\\\) essais et probabilit√© de succ√®s \\\\(2\\\\%\\\\). On sait de l\\'exercice pr√©c√©dent que \\\\(P(X_{20}\\\\geq 1) = 1 - (0.98)^{20}=0.33<0.80\\\\). On fait le m√™me calcul pour les autres valeurs de \\\\(n\\\\) propos√©es. On obtient \\\\( P(X_{70}\\\\geq 1)=1 - 0.98^{70}\\\\approx 0.75 \\\\), \\\\( P(X_{79}\\\\geq 1) = 1- 0.98^{79}\\\\approx 0.797\\\\), \\\\(P(X_{80}\\\\geq1) = 1-0.98^{80}\\\\approx0.801\\\\) et (pour le plaisir) \\\\(P(X_{90}\\\\geq1)=1-0.98^{90}\\\\approx0.838\\\\). Donc l\\'organisme devrait r√©aliser \\\\(80\\\\) inspections pour que la probabilit√© de d√©tecter au moins une violation soit sup√©rieure ou √©gale √† \\\\(0.8\\\\). Si on arrondit avant de comparer √† \\\\(0.80\\\\), alors on pourrait penser que \\\\(79\\\\) inspections sont suffisantes. Mais la probabilit√© avec ce nombre d\\'inspections est inf√©rieure √† \\\\(80 \\\\%\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n## Question 9\n\nSupposez maintenant que l‚Äôorganisme r√©alise \\\\(100\\\\) inspections ind√©pendantes, quelle est la probabilit√© de d√©tecter deux violations ou plus ? Les probabilit√©s sont arrondies au dixi√®me le plus proche.\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_LKWEBIFHUR'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_LKWEBIFHUR\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.60\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_LKWEBIFHUR\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.87\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_LKWEBIFHUR\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.40\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_LKWEBIFHUR\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.80\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Pensez √†  \\'\\'prendre la route la plus courte\\'\\'.', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, '\\\\(P(X\\\\geq 2) = 1- P(X=0)-P(X=1) = 1 - C^0_{100}(0.02)^0(0.98)^{100} - C^1_{100}(0.02)(0.98)^{99}\\\\) \\\\(= 1 - 0.98^{100} - 100\\\\cdot 0.02\\\\cdot 0.98^{99} \\\\approx 1 - 0.13 - 0.27 = 0.6\\\\). Revoir diapositives du cours \\\\(4\\\\), page \\\\(15\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n\n## Question 10\n\nPour la distribution standard normale \\\\(\\\\mathcal{N}(0,1)\\\\), combien vaut \\\\(\\\\Phi(0)\\\\)?\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_WBAVDGTDSL'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WBAVDGTDSL\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WBAVDGTDSL\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(1\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_WBAVDGTDSL\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.50\\\\)</span