ulative de densit√© de la distribution standard normale et calculez le compl√©ment.', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Soit \\\\(X \\\\sim \\\\mathcal{N}(0,1)\\\\), \\\\(P(X>0) = 1- \\\\Phi(0) = 1- 0.5 = 0.5\\\\).', 'explanation')\">\nüí° Explication\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n## Question 12\n\nSoit  \\\\(X \\\\sim \\\\mathcal{N}(0,1)\\\\), √† quoi correspond \\\\(P(X>1)\\\\)? Les probabilit√©s sont arrondies au dixi√®me le plus proche.\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_BXJASZXDXP'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BXJASZXDXP\" value=\"answer\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.16\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BXJASZXDXP\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.22\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BXJASZXDXP\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.84\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_BXJASZXDXP\" value=\"\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.75\\\\)</span></label></div>\n\n\n\n\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Consultez la table de la fonction cumulative de densit√© de la distribution standard normale et calculez le compl√©ment.', 'hint')\">\n‚ùì Indice\n</button>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin-top: 4px;\"></div>\n\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlert(event, 'Soit \\\\(X \\\\sim \\\\mathcal{N